des: This skill provides a random Trump quote. Just say "Alexa open Trump Quotes" to get started. Once the skill is open you can say "tell me a quote", "more", or "again" to hear another quote. All you need to get started is an Alexa enabled device.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
